@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using Entities;
@inject SignInManager<ApplicationUser> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<ApplicationUser> UserManager

<ul class="navbar-nav">
    @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
    {
        <li class="nav-item dropdown">
            <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="navbarDropdown" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                <i class="fas fa-user fa-lg fa-fw"></i>@User.Identity.Name
            </a>
            <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="navbarDropdown">
                <a asp-controller="Administration" asp-action="EditUser" asp-route-id="@UserManager.GetUserAsync(User).Result.Id" class="dropdown-item">Profile</a>
                <div class="dropdown-divider"></div>
                <a asp-controller="Account" asp-action="LogOut" class="dropdown-item">Log Out</a>
            </div>
        </li>
    }
    else
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text" style="color:grey" asp-area="" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">Register</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link text" style="color:grey" asp-area="" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="LogIn">LogIn</a>
        </li>
    }
</ul>
